	and dbgsyslog.c
	* mailbox/dbgstderr.c, mailbox/dbgsyslog.c: New files.
	* maidag/maidag.c, mail.local/main.c, sieve/sieve.c: Remove
	_mu_debug_printer, the default implementation will do.

	* mailbox/mu_auth.c: Improve debugging.
	
